{"tid":304152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國外交部：中英聯合聲明仍然有效，有法律約束力","createTime":"2017-06-30T16:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T00:59:07.000Z","uid":20933,"like":98,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"400f914dd960baf830081bff7c97d8895c817dc0","tid":304152,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170630/s00001/bfcfe238925c616f928ce4ca862a8884.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170630%2Fs00001%2Fbfcfe238925c616f928ce4ca862a8884.jpg&h=6d6f81fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國外交部今日在例行記者會上表示，1984年與英國簽署的《中英聯合聲明》是歷史文件，現在已「不再具有任何現實意義」。英國外交部回應指，《聲明》繼續生效，英國作為簽署國，有責任密切監督《聲明》實施情況。<br />\n<br />\n英國外交部發言人表示，《中英聯合聲明》是有法律約束力的條約，在聯合國有紀錄，《聲明》今日與30年前簽署時同樣有效，且會繼續生效，而英國作為聯合簽署國，有責任密切監督《聲明》實施情況。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人陸慷今日表示，《中英聯合聲明》「作為一個歷史文件，不再具有任何現實意義，對中國中央政府對香港特區的管理也不具備任何約束力。英方對回歸後的香港無主權、無治權、無監督權。」"},{"pid":"dea1cd3f73f761557d49bb733bd5a39a597d9c17","tid":304152,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:21:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170630/s00001/1498835919319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170630%2Fs00001%2F1498835919319&d=iKyNaObySeIne9ooppA8fjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e3240085\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170630%2Fs00001%2F1498835919319&h=f55f4537\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170630/s00001/1498835919319</a>"},{"pid":"64bb5e33f89fa5dcb3c9d2eb431584f7a309b71c","tid":304152,"uid":41742,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:24:07.000Z","msg":"約束力對中共有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b77f2aabfc32a087eaec20f3ff45be10da90a8c","tid":304152